HEADWORD: Fruitery
<hw>Fruit"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Fruiteries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[F. <ets>fruiterie</ets>
place where fruit is kept, in OF. also, <ets>fruitage</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
